    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rusted is a Linear horror game. You wake up from a coma, but something isn't right. Everything is worn down and there's rust everywhere. How long have you been out for? Figure out what happened and find your way out. But be careful, you're not alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles by picking up objects. Run, jump and crouch your way through the facility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WALL RUNNING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wall run to make your way out of the facility and through different sets of test chambers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/a66e628af724b894cdc54bc8d218653c.poster.avif?t=1745194041\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/a66e628af724b894cdc54bc8d218653c.webm?t=1745194041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/a66e628af724b894cdc54bc8d218653c.mp4?t=1745194041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up objects in the facility to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/999ef9699d5a07a9d7277311258caaf4.poster.avif?t=1745194041\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/999ef9699d5a07a9d7277311258caaf4.webm?t=1745194041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/999ef9699d5a07a9d7277311258caaf4.mp4?t=1745194041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PARKOUR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump and Sprint to explore your way out of the facility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/dbbafaac190ccbe582a75c2987e17063.poster.avif?t=1745194041\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/dbbafaac190ccbe582a75c2987e17063.webm?t=1745194041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229290/extras/dbbafaac190ccbe582a75c2987e17063.mp4?t=1745194041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY TIME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Est 45 - 60 minutes   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROADMAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will try to fix any bugs that occur</p>",
